# Mode B (Named Cloudflare Tunnel) requires a tunnel token from the
# Cloudflare dashboard:
#   1. https://one.dash.cloudflare.com/ → Networks → Tunnels
#   2. Create a tunnel; copy the token Cloudflare shows you.
#   3. cp share/.env.example share/.env
#   4. Paste the token below.
#
# share/.env is gitignored via the repo-wide *.env rule — your token
# never lands in git.
#
# Quick-tunnel mode (the default when you type `/remote tunnel on`)
# does NOT need this file. It's only for Mode B (stable hostname).
CF_TUNNEL_TOKEN=
